<span style="font-weight: bold;"><br>
The back story:&nbsp; </span>Gipf was the first of the project Gipf
series, but the last of the games to be added to Boardspace.&nbsp; How
odd is that?&nbsp; It's certainly the game in the series I understand
the least, but having the other 5, I had to complete the set.<br>
